For first time running only : 

python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt


To run environment : 

venv\Scripts\activate
python app.py


to run the training training.main_predict -> please make sure if you are deploying foing it properly :D !
python -m training.main_predict





To run the migration :" 

$env:FLASK_APP="main:app"
set FLASK_APP=main:app

flask db migrate -m "Initial migration"
flask db upgrade